===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|idiom}} A period of time, imagined never to end, in which (typically) a loving couple live untroubled, happy lives together.
#: {{syn|en|fairy-tale ending}}
#* {{quote-journal|en|work=AV Club|date=13 October 2020|author=Beatrice Loayza|title=Jack London gets an Italian makeover in the tragic and romantic ''Martin Eden''|passage=The couple’s romance, captured with intimate closeups and accompanied by a jaunty Europop soundtrack, is rapturous. But Martin’s increasingly provocative ideas throw a wrench in Elena’s dreams of a '''happily-ever-after'''.}}
# A story with such a happy ending, such as a [[romance]] novel or [[fairy tale]].

